// @utils/Constants.ts
export enum Colors {
  primary = '#f7ca49',
  primary_light = '#ffe141',
  secondary = '#0d8320',
  text = '#363636',
  whitetext = '#ffffff',
  disabled = '#9197a6',
  border = '#d0d4dc',
  blue = 'rgb(13, 107, 46)',
  color = 'rgba(2, 87, 37, 0.65)',
  lightcolor = 'rgba(2, 87, 37, 0.65)',
  backgroundSecondary = '#f5f6fb',
  success = '#28a745',
}

export enum Fonts {
  Regular = 'Okra-Regular',
  Medium =  "system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Arial, sans-serif",// âœ… use custom font
  Light = 'Okra-MediumLight',
  SemiBold = "system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Arial, sans-serif",
  Bold = 'Okra-ExtraBold',
}

export const lightColors = [
  'rgba(255,255,255,1)',
  'rgba(255,255,255,0.9)',
  'rgba(255,255,255,0.7)',
  'rgba(255,255,255,0.6)',
  'rgba(255,255,255,0.5)',
  'rgba(255,255,255,0.4)',
  'rgba(255,255,255,0.003)',
];

export const darkWeatherColors = [
  'rgba(54, 67, 92, 1)',
  'rgba(54, 67, 92, 0.9)',
  'rgba(54, 67, 92, 0.8)',
  'rgba(54, 67, 92, 0.2)',
  'rgba(54, 67, 92, 0)',
];
